snippet.title: The World Ends with You: Final Remix - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Neku and his partner must fight to survive a life-or-death game in this twisted tale with more turns than the urban labyrinth of Tokyo they’re trapped in. This definitive version of Square Enix’s RPG classic brings the dark story to life on the Nintendo Switch system along with an extra chapter, exclusive two-player combat, and some killer, new remixed music.

Learn more about The World Ends with You: Final Remix! https://goo.gl/XjgDmx

#NintendoSwitch #TWEWY
